---
description: Web app agent rules
globs: frontend/apps/web/**,frontend/packages/shared/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Read the root `AGENTS.md` first, then `frontend/AGENTS.md` for frontend work.

For web app tests, use pnpm from the repo root:

```bash
pnpm web:test -- run <testFileName>
```

To run all web tests:

```bash
pnpm web:test -- run
```

For shared package tests:

```bash
pnpm --filter @shm/shared test -- run <testFileName>
```

If a change is easily tested, add or update a test using the existing Vitest patterns.
